# WWW to non-WWW redirects (301 permanent)
https://www.textsnip.io/*  https://textsnip.io/:splat  301
http://www.textsnip.io/*   https://textsnip.io/:splat  301

# HTTP to HTTPS redirects (301 permanent)
http://textsnip.io/*       https://textsnip.io/:splat  301

